fights.name: Chopper
strategy: Summon Chopper by interacting with the coral
Run out of Charged Whisker, to avoid being paralyzed

fights.name: Captain Madison
strategy: AoE dogs down when they spawn at 50%

fights.name: Denn the Orcatoothed
strategy: When the gates in all four corners start bubbling, interact with them to prevent adds from spawning
If you're targeted by the adds, bring them to the tank

fights.name: Void Soulcounter
strategy: Spawns once the sealed barriers are brought down

fights.name: Galvanth the Dominator
strategy: Dodge the AoE telegraph, it causes paralyze
Kill the imps as soon as they come up
Once the imps are dead, kill the other adds
